      "rationale": "Linear elastic material model with plasticity for the titanium alloy screw is justified by the predominantly elastic response regime targeted by F1717. Contact formulation (augmented Lagrangian, friction coefficient 0.3) validated against published tribological data for Ti-6Al-4V on PEEK. Model form assumptions documented and peer-reviewed."
    },
    {
