      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties and geometric inputs must be traceable to measurements or certified material data sheets.",
      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V elastic modulus (114 GPa), yield strength (880 MPa), and UHMWPE block properties sourced from certified material test reports accompanying the test constructs. Screw geometry digitized from CMM measurements with ±5 µm tolerance. Input uncertainty propagated via Monte Carlo (n=1000); coefficient of variation <4% for all QoIs."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
