      "rationale": "All three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm) satisfy both acceptance criteria across all 11 specimens. E/uval values: stiffness 0.82, yield force 1.14, force at 40 mm 1.31. Maximum relative error 8.3%. Output comparison is fully satisfactory at gradation 3."
    },
